title: American Horror Story: Celebrating 100 Episodes With The AHS Cast
author: GameSpot Universe
comment: Which episode of American Horror Story is your all-time favorite?
I agree with Sarah Paulson about Evan Peters should have gotten ALL the awards for Cult!
Cody fern was so good as Michael Langdon
Cult is SO underrating and Evan Peters has shown his best acting skills in this season, he legit deserved every award in the world
I hope AHS goes forever, honestly
description:
Sarah Paulson talks Season 10, Ryan Murphy on the return of aliens and Leslie Grossman on what the stew tasted like. Join GameSpot Universe as we hit the American Horror Story red carpet to celebrate 100 Episodes of AHS. 

Subscribe to GameSpot Universe!
